Option **(1)** is the smaller change and matches the "smallest change that satisfies the task" rule. Option (2) better matches the PRD framing ("attached to the cast metadata" — `sdp/implementation-plan.md:47`).

Either way, the metadata shape to extend is the **per-element dict built at `duet_composer.py:396`** — adding a `sample` key (and probably `voice` nested under `voice` rather than spread, for clarity) is the natural extension.

